### P1-H · Checkbox yes/no logic — currently always checks every box
**File:** `__main__.py`, replace unconditional click at ~line 2329
**Impact:** High (form accuracy, prevents "Receive marketing email" / "I am unemployed" mistakes) | **Change:** 6 lines

```python
def should_check(label: str) -> bool:
    l = label.lower()
    if any(k in l for k in ["background check", "drug test", "terms", "authorize", "agree", "consent"]): return True
    if any(k in l for k in ["marketing", "newsletter", "promotional", "follow", "unemployed"]): return False
    return True  # default: check (conservative)

if not prev_answer and should_check(label_org):
